reviewText: Red Skelton was one of the funniest comedians on TV.  When watching his TV show, you could laugh from beginning to end.  This series of tapes was at the beginning of his career and was not funny (except for a few skits) and the quality was poor.  I would not recommend.
Everyone needs to laugh every day.  These videos of a wonderful comedian will bring a smile and even a giggle to your life.
